V4L2_PIX_FMT_GREY format is Ycbcr format without
the color data, therefore its pixel_enc should
set to V4L2_PIXEL_ENC_YUV.

Signed-off-by: Dafna Hirschfeld <dafna.hirschfeld@collabora.com>
---
